A sure way to help people relax at your year-end function and let their hair down is to put them behind a microphone to sing along to their favourite tune.Laughter is the best medicine for the end-of-year blow out. A comedy show is a good way to get people to loosen up.If you have a small business consider hosting a murder mystery party. These fun events give employees a unique experience that they will remember for a long time.Play for fun at casino-style gaming tables at your year-end event with play chips and play money supplied.These can be alcoholic or alcohol-free cocktails. Simply hire a professional mixologist to shake up some custom cocktail blends designed to suit the taste and personality of each staff member. Guests can dress up in classic cocktail wear.